advanced.paramOverridePlaceholder:
Optional, used to override request parameters. Does not support overriding stream parameter
Old format (direct override):
{
  "temperature": 0,
  "max_tokens": 1000
}

New format (supports conditions and json customization):
{
  "operations": [
    {
      "path": "temperature",
      "mode": "set",
      "value": 0.7,
      "conditions": [
        {
          "path": "model",
          "mode": "prefix",
          "value": "gpt"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

advanced.headerOverridePlaceholder:
Optional, used to override request headers
Format example:
{
  "User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/139.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/139.0.0.0",
  "Authorization": "Bearer {api_key}"
}
